channel.title: Need Help! Read edit of first post!
channel.description: I heard that if something could go wrong at portforwarding, it's something with static ip. What happends if there goes something wrong with the static ip? And how to fix it? And why will it happen? And in my home there are THREE computers using the SAME ROUTER. Will there be no problem if i set up an static ip if there are 3 computers using the same router? I use wireless internet.
